      DisplayName = "'...On the surface, we distinguished between aquatic creatures that live in the drinkable waters of rivers and lakes that dotted the terrain, and those of Lord Poseidon's salt-filled seas. In the former category, the Trout is a perfectly common breed, though here in the Underworld, it cannot be found...'"
